author: julianfoad
msg: Fix svndumpfilter's parsing of an empty path in the list of prefixes to be
included or excluded.  Previously if the empty path ('' or '/') was
specified, it didn't match any path whereas it should match all paths.
Add a test for this.  Also test the wildcard pattern '*' in pattern-matching
(ary_prefix_match): Fix the empty path case. Write a full doc string.
(skip_path): Document the form of the input paths.
